    <item>
      <title>MySQL Cheat Sheet</title>
      <link>https://wilfrantz.github.io/posts/2024-08-09-sql-cheatsheet/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 11:33:00 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://wilfrantz.github.io/posts/2024-08-09-sql-cheatsheet/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;MySQL&lt;/code&gt; is one of the most popular relational database management systems (&lt;code&gt;RDBMS&lt;/code&gt;) in the world. Whether you’re just starting out or you’re a seasoned developer, this cheat sheet will help you navigate MySQL more efficiently. This guide covers a broad spectrum of MySQL commands, functions, and tips that are essential for day-to-day database management.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;basic-mysql-commands&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;strong&gt;Basic MySQL Commands&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#basic-mysql-commands&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-database&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Create a Database&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#create-a-database&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; db_name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;select-a-database&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Select a Database&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#select-a-database&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;USE db_name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;show-databases&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Show Databases&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#show-databases&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;SHOW&lt;/span&gt; DATABASES;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;drop-a-database&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Drop a Database&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#drop-a-database&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;DROP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; db_name;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;show-tables-in-a-database&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Show Tables in a Database&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#show-tables-in-a-database&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;SHOW&lt;/span&gt; TABLES;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;describe-the-structure-of-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Describe the Structure of a Table&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#describe-the-structure-of-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;DESCRIBE&lt;/span&gt; tableName;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;table-operations&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;strong&gt;Table Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#table-operations&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Create a Table&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#create-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; tableName (&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    id INT &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;PRIMARY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt; AUTO_INCREMENT,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    name VARCHAR(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;),&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    age INT,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    email VARCHAR(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;);&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;show-the-table-schema&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Show the Table Schema&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#show-the-table-schema&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;SHOW&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; tableName;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;drop-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Drop a Table&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#drop-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;DROP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; tableName;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;rename-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Rename a Table&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#rename-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sql&#34; data-lang=&#34;sql&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;RENAME&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; old_tableName &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;TO&lt;/span&gt; newTableName;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;alter-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Alter a Table&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#alter-a-table&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Add a column:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Mastering C/C&#43;&#43; Library Development and Build Management with CMake</title>
      <link>https://wilfrantz.github.io/posts/2023-12-03-building-compiled-libraries/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2020 11:33:00 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://wilfrantz.github.io/posts/2023-12-03-building-compiled-libraries/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;When working on large &lt;code&gt;C/C++&lt;/code&gt; projects or creating reusable code, building compiled libraries is a common practice. Compiled libraries allow you to encapsulate functionality and data structures into reusable modules that can be easily linked into other programs.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In this blog post, we&amp;rsquo;ll walk you through the process of building a compiled library in &lt;code&gt;C/C++&lt;/code&gt; and show you how to prepare a &lt;code&gt;CMakeLists.txt&lt;/code&gt; file to manage the build process.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Table of Contents&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
